##
# Homebrew-cask
# https://github.com/phinze/homebrew-cask/blob/master/USAGE.md
#
##

# Make sure we're using the latest Homebrew
update

# Upgrade any all-ready installed formulae
upgrade

# Casks repository
tap phinze/homebrew-cask

# Homebrew-cask tool
install brew-cask

# Additional Casks repositories
tap caskroom/versions
tap caskroom/fonts

